headline: CASH COBAIN ANNOUNCES DEBUT HEADLINING TOUR
summary: Following a breakout year, rising rap star and producer Cash Cobain announces his first-ever headlining tour, The Monster Energy Outbreak Tour Presents: Party with Slizzy. The 23-date run kicks off September 7 in New York City and will hit major cities across the U.S. and Canada.
